  <entry>
    <title>对汇编的小理解</title>
    <link href="https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/04/%E5%AF%B9%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/"/>
    <id>https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/04/%E5%AF%B9%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</id>
    <published>2020-11-04T14:15:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-08T07:04:50.724Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="/images/2020110401.jpg" width="50%" height="50%"/><h4 id="用c-的方式来理解"><a href="#用c-的方式来理解" class="headerlink" title="用c++的方式来理解"></a>用c++的方式来理解</h4><p>mov ax,001AH -&gt; ax=001A (H表示16进制，001A是一位16进制数)<br>add ax,85H -&gt; ax+=85<br>add ax,bx -&gt; ax+=bx</p><h3 id="进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令"><a href="#进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令" class="headerlink" title="进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令"></a>进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令</h3><p>mov ax,bl (bl为8位寄存器，ax为16位寄存器)<br>mov al,20000 (al为8位寄存器，数据最大为2^8=256，0-255，而ax为16位寄存器，数据最大为2^16=65536,0-65535，均为十进制)<br>mov al,100H (100H已超出，16进制中1位相当于2进制中4位)</p><p>注意al和ah是构成ax的两个8位寄存器，我第一次看的时候没注意蒙了半天<br><img src="/images/2020110402.jpg" width="50%" height="50%"/></p><p>之前第一张图的代码用C++理解，代码如下(因为我对C++更熟悉)</p><ol><li>ax=001AH;</li><li>bx=0026H;</li><li>al+=bl;<h3 id="以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示"><a href="#以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示" class="headerlink" title="以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示"></a>以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示</h3>计算机应用课上自己打的代码…因为实在是…懂得都懂，输入两个十六进制数，输出它们相加的结果(注意是大写字母)<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> a[<span class="number">500</span>],b[<span class="number">500</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a1[<span class="number">500</span>],b1[<span class="number">500</span>],al,bl,i,max1,ans[<span class="number">500</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cin</span>&gt;&gt;a&gt;&gt;b;</span><br><span class="line">al=<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(a);</span><br><span class="line">bl=<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(b);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=al;i&gt;=<span class="number">1</span>;i--)a[i]=a[i<span class="number">-1</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=bl;i&gt;=<span class="number">1</span>;i--)b[i]=b[i<span class="number">-1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">max1=max(al,bl);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=max1+<span class="number">1</span>;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">a1[i]=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">b1[i]=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i]=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=al;i&gt;=<span class="number">1</span>;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(a[i]&gt;=<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;a[i]&lt;=<span class="string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>)a1[al-i+<span class="number">1</span>]=<span class="keyword">int</span>(a[i])-<span class="keyword">int</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(a[i]&gt;=<span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;a[i]&lt;=<span class="string">&#x27;F&#x27;</span>)a1[al-i+<span class="number">1</span>]=<span class="keyword">int</span>(a[i])<span class="number">-55</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=bl;i&gt;=<span class="number">1</span>;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(b[i]&gt;=<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;b[i]&lt;=<span class="string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>)b1[bl-i+<span class="number">1</span>]=<span class="keyword">int</span>(b[i])-<span class="keyword">int</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(b[i]&gt;=<span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;b[i]&lt;=<span class="string">&#x27;F&#x27;</span>)b1[bl-i+<span class="number">1</span>]=<span class="keyword">int</span>(b[i])<span class="number">-55</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//for(i=1;i&lt;=al;i++)cout&lt;&lt;a1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=max1;i++)ans[i]=a1[i]+b1[i];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//for(i=1;i&lt;=max1;i++)cout&lt;&lt;ans[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> h,j;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=max1;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">h=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(ans[i]&gt;=<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">h=ans[i]/<span class="number">16</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i]%=<span class="number">16</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i+<span class="number">1</span>]+=h;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(ans[max1+<span class="number">1</span>]!=<span class="number">0</span>)max1++;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//for(i=al;i&gt;=1;i--)cout&lt;&lt;a1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(i=max1;i&gt;=<span class="number">1</span>;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(ans[i]&gt;=<span class="number">0</span>&amp;&amp;ans[i]&lt;=<span class="number">9</span>)<span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;ans[i];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="built_in">cout</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="keyword">char</span>(ans[i]+<span class="number">55</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>输入样例：<br>4E20<br>406<br>输出样例:<br>5226</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
