    <title>待消化</title>
    <link href="https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/02/%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%81%E9%97%A8/"/>
    <id>https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/02/%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%81%E9%97%A8/</id>
    <published>2020-11-02T03:15:57.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-11-21T15:25:30.141Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="传送门"><a href="#传送门" class="headerlink" title="传送门"></a>传送门</h2><p><a href="https://yanyinhong.github.io/2017/05/02/How-to-insert-image-in-hexo-post/">在博客中插入图片</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/399e5a3c7cc5">markdown语法</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/heimu24/article/details/81189700#%E4%B8%80%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2">markdown进阶</a><br><a href="https://zhousiwei.gitee.io/2019/05/09/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2yilia%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90(%E7%BD%91%E6%98%93%E4%BA%91%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90)/">博客插入音乐</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/a0afac70afc8">博客置顶</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43039472/article/details/104391476">博客多标签</a></p><h3 id="在博客中插入图片"><a href="#在博客中插入图片" class="headerlink" title="在博客中插入图片"></a>在博客中插入图片</h3><p>在目录: blog\ (博客名) \ source \ images(自己创文件夹) 在该目录下存放图片文件并命名，如需引用即：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](&#x2F;images&#x2F;1.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是我目前用的最多的方法<br>2020.11.20 22:35</p><h3 id="调整图片大小"><a href="#调整图片大小" class="headerlink" title="调整图片大小"></a>调整图片大小</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;图片地址&quot; width&#x3D;&quot;50%&quot; height&#x3D;&quot;50%&quot;&#x2F;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实测有效，地址可以是本地地址。<br>2020.11.21 23:22</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
